To make cells count: i32, giving owned buffer of i32.
Let cells be owned buffer of count i32 filled with 0.
cells at 0 becomes 1.
cells at 1 becomes 2.
cells at 2 becomes 3.
cells at 3 becomes 4.
Give cells.

To consume index cells: owned buffer of i32 at i: i32, giving i32.
Give cells at i.

To main, giving i32.
Give consume index move (make cells 4) at 2.
